snippet.title: Tinkertown | Console Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Tinkertown Coming to Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One on October 17th and Nintendo Switch in November!

Grab a shovel, pickaxe, or sword and enter a world whole of treasures, magic, and dangers. Let your imagination run wild and create your own little fantasy kingdom - from a cozy adventurer's hut with a garden to a small town with NPCs and its own perks.

Wishlist it now on Xbox:
https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p9t08tgqskx
